  "texts": [
    "Some students (N = 5) mentioned that they did not fear or feel anxious when they used Metaverse-based technology while four students reported that they feared and felt anxious.",
    "Additionally, three participants stated that the flipped learning method supported by the Metaverse-based learning environment was effective in terms of visualization.",
    "On the other hand, three of the participants reported that the Metaverse-based online flipped classroom could be distractive during the learning process.",
    "However, two participants emphasized that online flipped learning assisted by Metaverse-based technology aroused their curiosity.",
    "P6: I have always found the Medical English course more enjoyable than the general English course."
  ]
}